############################################
### 2. 캠페인 수락 테스트 (creator 1 → campaign 1 or 3)
### campaign_acceptance.json  확인 결과:
### creator 1 은 campaign_id 1, 7, 9(accepted), campaign_id 2(rejected)
### → campaign 1,7,9 수락 테스트
############################################
POST https://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/creator/6/campaign/1/accept/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json



